  "texts": [
    "During the training process the labels are dynamically updated at the end of each epoch.",
    "The update rule for label L of the training example is the following:",
    "where α sets the shift from the current label to the new predicted label.",
    "At the beginning of training, L hard is the ground-truth label and later, it is the label computed in the previous epoch.",
    "L sof t is the predicted label after the training epoch is finished."
  ]
